.Sh NAME
.Nm sacd
.Nd simple anonymous chat daemon
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar port Op Ar address
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a server
that broadcasts all incoming messages
from any connection
to every other one.
To make messages atomic,
every client has read buffer
of 256 bytes.
so they won't overlap
while broadcast.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Ar port
Port to listen.
Default is
.Dv 8604 .
.It Ar address
Address to listen.
Default is
.Dv 0.0.0.0 .
.El
